// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-2577 — Mass File Rename (handala)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 4537ec52-4876-5043-b0c4-af860a56ebbd

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
